overview: A lot of liquor an whores, mustard and bologna, maybe some cigarettes and dope, but mostly just liquor and whores, cigarettes and balogna, as well as mustard and dope.

episodes.name: London
episodes.overview: The boys are excited to arrive in London until they learn they must execute weird tasks to earn spending money. First up: steal the queen's underwear.

episodes.name: Berlin
episodes.overview: The boys head to Berlin, where they must perform the "Chicken Dance" wearing lederhosen, take nude sunbathing selfies and run in the Berlin marathon.

episodes.name: Copenhagen
episodes.overview: In the capital of Denmark, the boys must climb into the boxing ring with a heavyweight champion and tour the city sporting a conspicuous sex device.

episodes.name: Oslo
episodes.overview: In Oslo, the boys are ordered to give an "atomic hover wedgie" to a cherished landmark and escort a local celebrity on a date to an ice bar.

episodes.name: Stockholm
episodes.overview: In Stockholm, the boys must eat a gut-busing meal of Swedish meatballs and fermented herring without barfing and make a save against a hockey legend.

episodes.name: Helsinki
episodes.overview: In a visit to Finland the boys meet the real Santa Claus, sing karaoke in a taxi, deliver a weather report and try their hands at ice sculpture.

episodes.name: Amsterdam 1
episodes.overview: The boys sport culturally traditional footwear, ride a three-person bicycle and visit a coffee shop while touring the capital of the Netherlands.
